text: Olena Haiasova (born 10 May 1969) is a Ukrainian cross-country skier. She competed in five events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Ukraine Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Vologda
